Class PromoSet

Object
MenuItem
PromoSet
public class PromoSet extends MenuItem
PromoSet is a subclass of MenuItem that only contains a list of ala carte items.

2021-11-3

    • PromoSet

      public PromoSet​(String name, String description, String price, String discount, String promoType, String itemList)
      Creates a new promotional set item with the parameters in String format. Used to read the menu text file. List of ala carte items is updated with the content of the menu text file.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of this promotional set.
      description - The description of this promotional set.
      price - The price of this promotional set.
      discount - The discount of this promotional set.
      promoType - The promo type of this promotional set.
      itemList - The list of ala carte items to be added into itemList.
